snippet.title: Game & Watch - Helmet (c)1981 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: Support for this will be in MAME 0.214, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork, with additional thanks to Mr. Do.  Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
